00:18:55.079 --> 00:19:05.079
I feel like I'm letting Jehovah down by feeling anxious and that I'm even being disobedient to Jesus when he says stop being anxious, but I just can't.

00:19:05.079 --> 00:19:07.079
Thank you for sharing that.

00:19:07.079 --> 00:19:12.079
Robert, what do you do to help Jordan battle this anxiety?

00:19:12.079 --> 00:19:17.079
It's a monster that sometimes a very stubborn monster that won't go away.

00:19:17.079 --> 00:19:30.079
Remembering that, remembering that it's not her fault that helps me be more compassionate, caring, listening when she's explaining these anxieties that I may not completely understand.

00:19:30.079 --> 00:19:34.079
Jordan, are there other practical things that help you battle anxiety?

00:19:34.079 --> 00:19:38.079
The single biggest help is walking with Jehovah every day.

00:19:38.079 --> 00:19:40.079
I mean that literally.

00:19:40.079 --> 00:19:50.079
I'll wake up in the morning, super anxious and I can't breathe and my chest is tight and I'll get up and I'll read the chapter of the Bible that the daily text comes from.

00:19:50.079 --> 00:19:57.079
And then I'll go on a walk and talk to Jehovah for an hour and I try to use the model prayer as an outline.

00:19:57.079 --> 00:20:04.079
So I'll talk to Jehovah about his name and how I feel so privileged to have that name on me.

00:20:04.079 --> 00:20:11.079
And I'll talk to him about his kingdom that's going to solve all of these problems, including anxiety.

00:20:11.079 --> 00:20:18.079
And I'll talk to him about his will and specifically what his will is for me that day.

00:20:18.079 --> 00:20:23.079
And most of the time, those three things cover the things that were worrying me.

00:20:23.079 --> 00:20:27.079
But if there is another thing, I'll talk to him specifically about that.

00:20:27.079 --> 00:20:29.079
What a nice walk you have with Jehovah.

00:20:29.079 --> 00:20:33.079
Are there other things that help you deal and battle anxiety?

00:20:33.079 --> 00:20:37.079
Personal study projects help a lot, especially if they don't have anything to do with anxiety.

00:20:37.079 --> 00:20:45.079
If I do a study project on the spiritual suit of armor or the ransom, it kind of distracts the anxiety monster.

00:20:45.079 --> 00:20:47.079
So my heart can calm down.

00:20:47.079 --> 00:20:52.079
And then these pearls of wisdom will come from Jehovah and they can get in.

00:20:52.079 --> 00:20:56.079
And if some of those pearls are actually just what I need to deal with my anxiety.

00:20:56.079 --> 00:20:59.079
Are there specific things that help you?

00:20:59.079 --> 00:21:05.079
Yes. I made an anxiety tab in the personal study section of my study Bible on my tablet.

00:21:05.079 --> 00:21:10.079
And I collect scriptures and comments that really help with my anxiety.

00:21:10.079 --> 00:21:20.079
For example, in 2014, there was a regional convention talk about Matthew chapter six and six specific things that combat anxiety.

00:21:20.079 --> 00:21:25.079
And it made me think of like the 12-step program to overcoming addiction.

00:21:25.079 --> 00:21:27.079
This is the six steps to overcoming anxiety.

00:21:27.079 --> 00:21:29.079
What are those six steps?

00:21:29.079 --> 00:21:39.079
The first one is to help those in need and then pray a lot to be forgiving, not to be hypocritical, to store up treasures in heaven,

00:21:39.079 --> 00:21:42.079
and then to focus on spiritual matters.

00:21:42.079 --> 00:21:46.079
So when we got back from the convention, she took those items.

00:21:46.079 --> 00:21:49.079
She wrote them down and put them on magnets and put them on our refrigerator.

00:21:49.079 --> 00:21:52.079
I try to do each one of those six things every day.

00:21:52.079 --> 00:21:57.079
