To serve at Bethel, there are qualifications that need to be met.

00:48:02.440 --> 00:48:06.440
You should have a deep love for Jehovah in the organization

00:48:06.440 --> 00:48:10.440
which is demonstrated by living in harmony with Bible standards.

00:48:10.440 --> 00:48:15.440
You must have a fine reputation as a spiritual person.

00:48:15.440 --> 00:48:18.440
You should have respect for Jehovah's moral standards

00:48:18.440 --> 00:48:22.440
of audience uncleanness and sexual immorality.

00:48:22.440 --> 00:48:25.440
You should have a clean conscience before Jehovah

00:48:25.440 --> 00:48:30.440
and be at peace with yourself and with Jehovah's organization.

00:48:30.440 --> 00:48:33.440
Your dress and grooming should be exemplary.

00:48:33.440 --> 00:48:37.440
Be fitting a Christian minister even during leisure time.

00:48:37.440 --> 00:48:40.440
Styles that are fatish or extreme

00:48:40.440 --> 00:48:44.440
or that identify us with undesirable elements of the world

00:48:44.440 --> 00:48:47.440
are not acceptable at Bethel.

00:48:47.440 --> 00:48:52.440
The applicant would not read, listen to or view any type of material

00:48:52.440 --> 00:48:55.440
that is inappropriate for a Christian.

00:48:55.440 --> 00:48:59.440
Such unhost some material certainly would include pornography,

00:48:59.440 --> 00:49:05.440
debasing music, or any kind of entertainment that features sexual immorality,

00:49:05.440 --> 00:49:08.440
spiritism, or violence.

00:49:08.440 --> 00:49:13.440
Bethel applicants should be from 19 to 35 years of age.

00:49:13.440 --> 00:49:18.440
Occasionally, there is an opening for someone over 35 years of age

00:49:18.440 --> 00:49:22.440
who may have specialized skills that are needed at Bethel,

00:49:22.440 --> 00:49:26.440
such as those with certain technical or medical experience,

00:49:26.440 --> 00:49:31.440
translation skills, or building trades such as plumbing, electrical,

00:49:31.440 --> 00:49:35.440
heavy equipment mechanic, or carpentry.

00:49:35.440 --> 00:49:40.440
Those with such capabilities and training are welcome to apply.

00:49:40.440 --> 00:49:44.440
In view of the unique demands of a full-time assignment at Bethel,

00:49:44.440 --> 00:49:49.440
you should be mentally and emotionally sound, physically strong,

00:49:49.440 --> 00:49:52.440
and able to work long hours.

00:49:52.440 --> 00:49:58.440
You should be able to read, write, and speak the primary language of the branch territory.

00:49:58.440 --> 00:50:02.440
This will enable you to communicate well with others serving at Bethel

00:50:02.440 --> 00:50:08.440
to receive needed training and to work safely in the Bethel environment.

00:50:08.440 --> 00:50:12.440
Bethel applicants agreed to serve for a minimum of one year,

00:50:12.440 --> 00:50:18.440
during which time you will receive training for continued Bethel service.

00:50:18.440 --> 00:50:21.440
With regard to secular skills,

00:50:21.440 --> 00:50:26.440
we do not encourage individuals to obtain university education or training

00:50:26.440 --> 00:50:30.440
with a thought that this will improve their chances of being called into Bethel.

00:50:30.440 --> 00:50:37.440
The best way to prepare for Bethel service is to first serve in the full-time pioneer ministry.

00:50:37.440 --> 00:50:41.440
The greatest need is for single brothers.

00:50:41.440 --> 00:50:45.440
However, all who meet the qualifications, including sisters,

00:50:45.440 --> 00:50:49.440
are encouraged to apply for temporary volunteer service.

00:50:49.440 --> 00:50:53.440
Serving as a temporary volunteer at Bethel may open the way to other opportunities

00:50:53.440 --> 00:50:56.440
to expand your service to Jehovah.

00:50:56.440 --> 00:51:00.440
If you are interested in applying for Bethel service,

00:51:00.440 --> 00:51:05.440
which application should you request from a member of your congregation service committee?

00:51:05.440 --> 00:51:09.440
Since there are two types of applications available,

00:51:09.440 --> 00:51:14.440
first, give careful and prayerful consideration to your circumstances.

00:51:14.440 --> 00:51:20.440
Thereafter, decide whether you will request from the elders the application for volunteer program,

00:51:20.440 --> 00:51:25.440
A19, which is available for those interested in serving on a temporary basis

00:51:25.440 --> 00:51:30.440
